---
const accent = "#C9A646";
---

<section id="about" class="text-white antialiased py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Main heading -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-[39.2px] font-medium tracking-wide">About Us</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-[22.4px] font-medium tracking-wide" style={`color:${accent}`}>
        Engineering the Future, One Nextstep at a Time
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Intro paragraph -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-[18.2px] leading-relaxed text-white/90">
        At Nextstep, we believe innovation begins with precision — and precision
        begins with people who care about the details. Founded on German
        engineering standards and strengthened by an international network of
        experts, we bring world-class software solutions to life with
        reliability, creativity, and trust. Our mission is simple: to help
        businesses take their next step toward smarter, faster, and safer
        digital transformation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Our Story Card -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12">
        <h3 class="text-[22.4px] font-medium tracking-wide text-center mb-6">Our Story</h3>
        <p class="text-[18.2px] leading-relaxed text-white/90 text-center">
          Nextstep was founded with a clear vision — to bridge the gap between
          engineering excellence and modern software development. What started as
          a small collaboration between engineers and developers has evolved into
          a global technology partner trusted by clients across industries. From
          aerospace systems to digital platforms, we deliver solutions where
          failure is not an option — and precision is a promise.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Vision & Mission -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
        <!-- Our Vision -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 p-8 sm:p-10 text-center">
          <h3 class="text-[22.4px] font-medium tracking-wide mb-6">Our Vision</h3>
          <p class="text-[18.2px] italic leading-relaxed text-white/90">
            "To be the trusted engineering partner that transforms innovation
            into reliable solutions for the world's most demanding industries."
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Our Mission -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 p-8 sm:p-10 text-center">
          <h3 class="text-[22.4px] font-medium tracking-wide mb-6">Our Mission</h3>
          <p class="text-[18.2px] italic leading-relaxed text-white/90">
            "We combine engineering discipline with software intelligence to
            design, develop, and deliver solutions that enable progress,
            performance, and peace of mind."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Core Values -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-[22.4px] font-medium tracking-wide text-center mb-8">Our Core Values</h3>
      <div class="text-[18.2px]">
        <!-- First row: Precision and Collaboration -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 p-6">
            <span class="font-medium block mb-2" style={`color:${accent}`}>Precision</span>
            <span class="text-white/90">
              Every detail matters — our work follows the highest engineering
              standards.
            </span>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 p-6">
            <span class="font-medium block mb-2" style={`color:${accent}`}>Collaboration</span>
            <span class="text-white/90">
              Our clients are partners — we grow together through shared goals.
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Second row: Innovation and Reliability -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 p-6">
            <span class="font-medium block mb-2" style={`color:${accent}`}>Innovation</span>
            <span class="text-white/90">
              We explore emerging technologies to create meaningful progress.
            </span>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 p-6">
            <span class="font-medium block mb-2" style={`color:${accent}`}>Reliability</span>
            <span class="text-white/90">
              When performance matters most, we deliver with confidence.
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Third row: Integrity full width -->
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 p-6">
          <span class="font-medium block mb-2" style={`color:${accent}`}>Integrity</span>
          <span class="text-white/90">
            We build trust through transparency, consistency, and
            accountability.
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Global Perspective & Commitment -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
        <!-- Our Global Perspective -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 p-8 sm:p-10">
          <h3 class="text-[22.4px] font-medium tracking-wide mb-6">
            Our Global Perspective
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[18.2px] leading-relaxed text-white/90">
            With roots in Germany and a strong presence in Thailand, Nextstep
            operates at the intersection of European quality and Asian
            adaptability. This dual foundation allows us to deliver precise,
            scalable, and cost-effective software solutions tailored to each
            client's unique business environment.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Our Commitment -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 p-8 sm:p-10">
          <h3 class="text-[22.4px] font-medium tracking-wide mb-6">
            Our Commitment
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[18.2px] leading-relaxed text-white/90">
            Nextstep is more than a software company — we are your long-term
            technology partner. We are committed to continuous improvement,
            certified excellence, and measurable impact in every project we
            deliver.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-6 text-[18.2px] italic leading-relaxed" style={`color:${accent}`}>
            "Your success is not our goal — it's our foundation."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
